FBIS4-37622 "drnes121_l_94014" FBIS-NES-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 ISRAEL Security Forces Uncover Samaria Islamic Jihad Group Security Forces Uncover Samaria Islamic Jihad Group TA2206164594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 22 Jun 94 TA2206164594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Text] In Qalqilyah in western Samaria security forces have captured an Islamic Jihad terror band. The five members are suspected of being involved in the murder of an alleged collaborator with Israel in the center of Qalqilyah several days ago. Security forces also seized three weapons, including the gun which belonged to the murdered man. One suspected member of the band is believed to have fled and taken refuge in Jericho.
